import React from 'react'
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'reactstrap'

const location = () => (
    <section className="gym locations" id="plan">
        <Container>
            <Row>
                <Col lg="4" md="4" className="offset-md-2 offset-lg-0">

                </Col>
            </Row>
        </Container>
    </section>
)


export default location;
